Task 1: Portfolio Website
Objective

Design and develop a personal portfolio website to showcase projects, skills, and contact information with a clean, professional, and responsive UI.

Implementation

Technology stack: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Tailwind CSS (for styling).

Features implemented:

Home page with introduction and personal details.

Projects section with cards showcasing completed works.

About section highlighting skills, education, and experience.

Contact form for communication.

Design choices:

Light color theme for professional aesthetics.

Responsive grid-based layout using Tailwind CSS.

Project cards with images and hover effects.

Impact

Created a professional online presence.

Improved UI/UX with responsive design for mobile and desktop.

Portfolio serves as a showcase for recruiters and clients.
